reviewText: Buscar esta pelicula..estaba en chino!! I was looking for this movie..luis miguel y lucerito..2 jovenes talentos!!
It brought back memories of watching this as a kid. It's a cute story.
IT KEEPS  PEOPLE INTERESTED TO WATCH WHATS GOING TO HAPPEN NEXT  NOT A  BAD  MOVIE  JUST SIT BACK  AND  WATCH THE SHOW
